<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Roomz</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/index.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/Grid.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <h1>
          <a class="bttn3" href="/"><ion-icon name="tv"></ion-icon>Roomz</a>
        </h1>
        <ul>
          <% if(user != null) { %>
          <li>
            <p class="wel">Welcome,&nbsp;</p>
            <p class="nm"><%= user.name %></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
              <button type="submit" class="bttn2">Log Out</button>
            </form>
          </li>
          <% } else { %>
          <li>
            <a class="bttn2" href="/auth">Login<span> | </span>Signup</a>
          </li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <div class="text-box">
        <h1><span>Roomz</span> - A New Video Calling App For All!</h1>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>
          We re-engineered the service we built for secure business meetings,
          Roomz, to make it free and available to all.
        </p>
        <br />
        <a class="bttn" href="/meeting">Join or Create a Room Now</a>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="scroll">Scroll down</div> -->
    </header>

    <!--**************Features*****************-->
    <section class="features">
      <div class="row">
        <h2>Premium Features</h2>
        <p class="long-copy">
          <center>Here are some of our latest and greatest features.</center>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row n">
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 box">
          <ion-icon name="people" class="icon-big"></ion-icon>
          <h3>Feature 1</h3>
          <p>
            Learn all the recommended Interview questions by our community.
            Contribute your Interview experiences and questions with the
            community. Be a part our rapidly growing community.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 box">
          <ion-icon name="happy-outline" class="icon-big"></ion-icon>
          <h3>Feature 2</h3>
          <p>
            Get truly insightful and first-hand interview experiences stright
            from our community, which will give you the necessary boost for your
            next interview. Share your experience here as well.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 box">
          <ion-icon name="pencil-outline" class="icon-big"></ion-icon>
          <h3>Feature 3</h3>
          <p>
            Learn the topics essential for craking the coding interview and also
            for competitive programming. We also tell the recommended topics
            that you require to learn.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!--**************Testimonials*****************-->
    <section class="testimonials">
      <div class="row">
        <h2>Our Users Are Loving Us</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="row testimonials-text">
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 go">
          <blockquote>
            Wow! Never thought i would get such an addiction from using the app
            due to its ease to use and user friendly UI. Just loved it at first
            sight itself. It works seamlessly without any fuss and that too
            securing my privacy.
          </blockquote>
          <br />
          <cite><img src="img/customer-1.jpg" alt="Cutomer-1" /> Ritik</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 go">
          <blockquote>
            It's whiteboard feature just stands out amongst its competitors. Its
            super smooth, even in bad connectivity. The app is super efficient
            and is easy to use. It works really well with low band-width
            scenarios as well.
          </blockquote>
          <br />
          <cite><img src="img/customer-2.png" alt="Cutomer-2" /> Akansha </cite>
        </div>
        <div class="col span-1-of-3 go">
          <blockquote>
            This app has proved to be very helpful during these tough times of
            covid. It's video calling feature has been a boon for me. The user
            experience has been lovely from the start itself. Its my always a go
            to app for my teaching purposes.
          </blockquote>
          <br />
          <cite><img src="img/customer-3.png" alt="Cutomer-3" /> Karan </cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->

    <footer>
      <div class="row">
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li>
            Learn more about the people who made this app! -
            <a href="/contact-us">About Us</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="footer-social">
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="facebook"
              ><ion-icon name="logo-facebook"></ion-icon
            ></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="twitter"
              ><ion-icon name="logo-twitter"></ion-icon
            ></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="youtube"
              ><ion-icon name="logo-youtube"></ion-icon
            ></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="instagram"
              ><ion-icon name="logo-instagram"></ion-icon
            ></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <p>Copyright &copy; Roomz - Video Call. All rigths reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script
      type="module"
      src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.esm.js"
    ></script>
    <script
      nomodule
      src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.js"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
